<br>
telnet://harf.no-ip.com<br>
http://www.mitcharf.com/~bbs/<br>
<br>
Harf! features the following door games: Barren Realms Elite*, Trade Wars*, Legend of the Red Dragon*, The Pit*, Pimp Wars, Murder Motel, Kannons & Katapults, Boggle, and Word Eliminate (* indicates the game is registered)..<br>
<br>
