<br>
One thing that did surprise me, though, is the number of young callers I am getting.  I figured I wouldn't get many people under the age of 20 calling, because they probably don't remember when BBSes were popular.  But I've had quite a few callers in that age range, so I'm not sure how to explain it.<br>
<br>
